article_title: Earthquake Strikes Near Fairview - News9.com - Oklahoma City, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports
article_text:
Another sizeable earthquake struck Oklahoma overnight.

This quake, a 3.9 magnitude, rattled the ground 17 miles northwest of Fairview and 38 miles east of Woodward. It was approximately five miles deep.

No damage or injuries were immediately reported.
